article_title: Q&A with Eric Knowles, president of the Miami-Dade Chamber of Commerce
article_text: A new building, a master plan for the county’s urban core, and making the Miami-Dade Chamber of Commerce relevant to young black professionals are among the goals of G. Eric Knowles, who now leads the Miami-Dade Chamber of Commerce.
